</entry><entry thead="no"><para><emphasis>(none)</emphasis>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Type-erased base for polymorphic sparse set access  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>View&lt;TEntityManager, Components...&gt;</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Manager type, component types  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Lightweight component-based entity queries  </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
</sect2>
