</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_cd6c3d957c65ac83604a28625a3bf9a1_1autotoc_md102">
<title>Template Parameter Overview</title><para>The move from <computeroutput><ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1engine_1_1ecs" kindref="compound">helios.engine.ecs</ref></computeroutput> to <computeroutput><ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1ecs" kindref="compound">helios.ecs</ref></computeroutput> introduced the following <bold>new</bold> template parameters:</para>
<para><table rows="8" cols="3"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>Parameter  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Used In  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Purpose  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>TStrongId</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>EntityHandle</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>EntityRegistry</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Domain-specific strong ID type satisfying <computeroutput>IsStrongIdLike</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>THandle</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>EntityManager</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Entity</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>ComponentTypeId</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>ComponentOpsRegistry</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>ComponentReflector</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>The concrete <computeroutput>EntityHandle&lt;TStrongId&gt;</computeroutput> specialisation, scoping type IDs and ops per domain  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>TEntityRegistry</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>EntityManager</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>The concrete <computeroutput>EntityRegistry</computeroutput> specialisation used for handle allocation  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>TEntityManager</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>Entity</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>View</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>EntityResolver</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>ComponentReflector</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>The concrete <computeroutput>EntityManager</computeroutput> specialisation providing component storage  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>TLookupStrategy</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>EntityRegistry</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Pluggable collision detection strategy for strong IDs  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>TAllowRemoval</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>EntityRegistry</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>bool</computeroutput> policy — <computeroutput>false</computeroutput> disables <computeroutput>destroy()</computeroutput> at compile time  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>TCapacity</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>EntityRegistry</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>EntityManager</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Default initial capacity hint  </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_cd6c3d957c65ac83604a28625a3bf9a1_1autotoc_md103">
<title>TypedHandleWorld</title><para><computeroutput>TypedHandleWorld&lt;TEntityManagers...&gt;</computeroutput> is a <bold>multi-domain entity world</bold> that holds one <computeroutput>EntityManager</computeroutput> per domain inside a <computeroutput>std::tuple</computeroutput>. The handle type of each manager serves as a compile-time key: calling <computeroutput>world.addEntity&lt;MyHandle&gt;()</computeroutput> selects the correct manager automatically.</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">using<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">GameHandle<sp/>=<sp/>EntityHandle&lt;GameStrongId&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">using<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">UiHandle<sp/><sp/><sp/>=<sp/>EntityHandle&lt;UiStrongId&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">using<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">GameEM<sp/>=<sp/>EntityManager&lt;GameHandle,<sp/>GameRegistry,<sp/>4096&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">using<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">UiEM<sp/><sp/><sp/>=<sp/>EntityManager&lt;UiHandle,<sp/><sp/><sp/>UiRegistry,<sp/><sp/><sp/>512&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">TypedHandleWorld&lt;GameEM,<sp/>UiEM&gt;<sp/>world;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>player<sp/>=<sp/>world.addEntity&lt;GameHandle&gt;();<sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>→<sp/>GameEM</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>button<sp/>=<sp/>world.addEntity&lt;UiHandle&gt;();<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>→<sp/>UiEM</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_cd6c3d957c65ac83604a28625a3bf9a1_1autotoc_md104">
<title>Quick Start</title><para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">import</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="module__helios_8ecs" kindref="compound">helios.ecs</ref>;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>1.<sp/>Define<sp/>domain<sp/>types</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">struct<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">MyStrongId<sp/>{<sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">/*<sp/>...<sp/>*/</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">using<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">Handle<sp/><sp/><sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="structhelios_1_1ecs_1_1types_1_1EntityHandle" kindref="compound">helios::ecs::types::EntityHandle&lt;MyStrongId&gt;</ref>;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">using<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">Registry<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="classhelios_1_1ecs_1_1EntityRegistry" kindref="compound">helios::ecs::EntityRegistry&lt;MyStrongId&gt;</ref>;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">using<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">Manager<sp/><sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="classhelios_1_1ecs_1_1EntityManager" kindref="compound">helios::ecs::EntityManager&lt;Handle, Registry, 1024&gt;</ref>;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>2.<sp/>Create<sp/>manager<sp/>and<sp/>entity</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Manager<sp/>em;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>handle<sp/>=<sp/>em.<ref refid="classhelios_1_1ecs_1_1EntityManager_1aab954201f74e12cf29d2b961c8708a2f" kindref="member">create</ref>();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>3.<sp/>Attach<sp/>components</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal">*<sp/>transform<sp/>=<sp/>em.emplace&lt;TransformComponent&gt;(handle,<sp/>position);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>4.<sp/>Use<sp/>the<sp/>Entity<sp/>facade</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classhelios_1_1ecs_1_1Entity" kindref="compound">helios::ecs::Entity&lt;Handle, Manager&gt;</ref><sp/>entity{handle,<sp/>&amp;em};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">entity.<ref refid="classhelios_1_1ecs_1_1Entity_1a6d53d9ccd082d76aff6870f4fb83db36" kindref="member">add</ref>&lt;HealthComponent&gt;(100.0f);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>5.<sp/>Iterate<sp/>via<sp/>View</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">for</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>[e,<sp/>t,<sp/>v]<sp/>:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><ref refid="classhelios_1_1ecs_1_1View" kindref="compound">helios::ecs::View&lt;Manager, TransformComponent, VelocityComponent&gt;</ref>(&amp;em))<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>process</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
